data.description: Beautiful home in Smith Valley on Day Lane. The master bedroom is quite large with a walk-in-closet, and large master bath with jetted tub, shower and double sinks and secluded from the other bedrooms. The great room has a gas fireplace with a river rock finish. The formal dining room sits off in its own area and has room to open up for quite a large dining table. The laundry room has all the amenities including laundry sink, cabinets and a half bath. Then the upstairs over the garage is a bonus room which is the 4th bedroom and large enough to be the games room or craft room for your hobbies. The home has been freshly painted exterior with a great front porch to enjoy your morning coffee and afternoon cocktails. Nice lawn and lots of trees and bushes. A large shed along side the west side of the home matches house paint and is kind of hidden. A kabota LX2610 tractor with implements is negotiable.  Motivated sellers submit all offers Only home available with 20 aces for all your animals and workshop.
